{"tid":1780092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再長他人志氣，「傻強」係我眼中就只係一個懶醒嘅傻仔","createTime":"2019-12-12T06:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T09:33:26.000Z","uid":9824,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e22fac2e345a2efb5645432d5233a68ec89ebe00","tid":1780092,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"要對付佢，首先再針對翻佢個人嘅弱點。<br />\n暫時見到傻強條友其中一個特點係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「愛出風頭」</span><br />\n佢係第一個成日見記者，仲會落場視察嘅曱甴皇。<br />\n針對翻佢依樣野，大家可以用盡任何方法落佢面。<br />\n<br />\n唔大家有無睇「火鳳燎原」。依家打緊仗，一直以<br />\n來大家講嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「溫度」</span></span>，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「士氣」</span></span>。要切記再長他人志氣，要識「貶敵抬己」。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家講到個個都知佢有料，講到連佢班曱甴仔都覺得<br />\n佢真係有料，佢地就士氣大勇</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有針對翻佢好撚要面嘅特點，大大力諗盡方法落佢面，（例如：貼佢個狗樣落連儂牆，或者更加激進更加直接嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令到佢地諗嘅策略無效，地下化勇武攻其不備，我地做到嘢但佢又拉唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）佢就會開始亂</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家可以係連登做嘅就係唔好再推，吹奏隻傻強好撚勁嘅post同善用不推文回覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"938f30087b5189f39b2bb04d9e90aea8a70c41da","tid":1780092,"uid":199332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"啱，吹奏佢做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同動搖中嘅淺黃朋友傾計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780052</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8042f902185c74ea6e893b5804552b53985d018","tid":1780092,"uid":171742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:15:11.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"428f3de1f5358fd51e4576451495a26ec73b383d","tid":1780092,"uid":269515,"like":9,"dislike":0,"s